description:
We launched a Patreon! https://www.patreon.com/justoneepisode 


Just One Episode drops weekly to subscribers. The best way we can explain it? Imagine if Jackie and I launched a new podcast every week, and then never did another episode of that podcast again. But then next week, there’d be a new podcast, with a new theme song and new topics. Patreon subscribers aka The Mountain Dew Producers Circle (#notspon) get access to every episode, plus bonus content, photos of behind the scenes during mini recording sessions, and a secret instagram account. We want to see you there! (There’s also a $2 Palette Patrons level if you don’t need a new podcast but you want to support the minis!)


***


On this mini, we go through our bags, and the exercise reveals a lot about Jackie. Like, it’s scary.


Mentioned On This Episode!

  • Kindle Paperwhite Waterproof: https://amzn.to/3CAVyzh 
  • Hyer Goods: https://hyergoods.com/ 
  • Anker Airpods: https://amzn.to/3CzKHWn 
  • She’s Birdie Alarm (GeeThanks10 for 10% off your order): https://www.shesbirdie.com/ 
  • Matt and Nat bags: https://fave.co/3xxhrvv
